title: Visitor Privileges & Resources: Libraries - Northwestern University
content: Visiting from out of town? We welcome library tours and high school class visits to the Libraries. Scheduling is subject to staff and space availability and the University's academic calendar. Please note that we may only be able to accommodate limited group sizes for visits. Inquire about instruction for your class or group via the library instruction request form. To apply for borrowing privileges, please fill an application. Apply now Borrowing privileges do not give borrowers off-campus access to subscription services, due to site-licensing agreements. Borrowing card holders are not eligible to use the Library's Interlibrary Loan or Scan & Deliver services.
